Occurring along the east coast from south of the Masoala Peninsula to Taolagnaro. Present in: Amparafaravola District, Alaotra-Mangoro Region, Soanierana Ivongo and Fenoarivo Atsinanana Districts, Analanjirofo Region, and, Vatomandry District, Atsinanana Region (
Toamasina Province
); Midongy-Atsimo District, Atsimo-Atsinanana Region (
Fianarantsoa Province
); Taolagnaro District, Anosy Region (
Toliara Province
) (
Fig. 23C
).

